import React from "react";
import {Box, Typography, styled, Button, Stack} from "@mui/material"
import Background from "./../Images/HeroBackground.jpg";
import Handy from "./../Images/handy.png";

const RightBox = styled(Box)({
    backgroundImage:`url(${Background})`, 
    backgroundAttachment: "fixed",
    backgroundSize: "100%",
    minHeight:"80vh",
    textAlign: "right",
    alignItems: "right",
    alignContent: "right",
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    justifyContent: "end",
});

const Header = styled(Stack)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    textAlign: "left",
    textOverflow: "ellipsis",
    alignItems: "center",
    gap: "2px",
});

const StyledButton = styled(Button)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    color: "black",
    alignSelf: "right",
    maxWidth: "110px",
    borderRadius: theme.shape.borderRadius,
});

const WhiteText = styled(Typography)({
    color: "white",
});

const GreenText = styled(Typography)({
    color: "#BFD200",
});

//StyledBox als Parent von LeftBox und RIghtBox?
export default function Hero() {
    return (
        <Stack bgcolor="black">
            <Stack direction="row">
                <Box flex={1}
                    component="img"
                    src={require("../Images/handy.png")}
                    sx={{maxHeight:"100%"}}>
                </Box>
                <Stack direction="column" flex={2}>
                    <Header direction="row">
                        <Typography variant="h4">
                            DEIN DIGITALER 
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{fontWeight:"bold", p:"5px"}}>
                            CO-TRAINER
                        </Typography>
                    </Header>
                    <RightBox>
                        <GreenText>
                            COACHING MADE EASY
                        </GreenText>
                        <WhiteText fontSize="2.5rem">
                            MINIMALER AUFWAND.
                        </WhiteText>
                        <WhiteText fontSize="2.5rem" sx={{fontWeight:"bold"}}>
                            MAXIMALER ERFOLG.
                        </WhiteText>
                        <WhiteText>
                            Weil der Trainerjob Spa√ü machen soll!
                        </WhiteText>
                        <StyledButton>
                            LOS GEHT'S
                        </StyledButton>
                        <Stack direction="row">
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <WhiteText>
                                    6.000+
                                </WhiteText>
                                <WhiteText>
                                    Trainer
                                </WhiteText>
                            </Stack>
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <WhiteText>
                                    5 Mio
                                </WhiteText>
                                <WhiteText>
                                    Trainings
                                </WhiteText>
                            </Stack>
                            <Stack direction="column">
                                <WhiteText>
                                    3.000+
                                </WhiteText>
                                <WhiteText>
                                    Spiele
                                </WhiteText>
                            </Stack>
                        </Stack>
                    </RightBox>
                </Stack>
            </Stack>
        </Stack>
    )
}
